{
  "texts": [
    "We remind the reader that our data has survivorship bias and uses synthetic (but realistic) mean return forecasts, so the performance should not be thought of as implementable.",
    "But the differences in performance of the different trading methods is significant.",
    "In this section we show how parameter tuning can be used to improve the performance of the portfolio construction method.",
    "We will tune the parameters γ hold, γ trade, γ lev, γ risk, and γ turn, keeping the other parameters fixed.",
    "We start from the values used in Markowitz++."
  ]
}